**Article 2. Implementation**

1\. This Decree comes into force from November 25, 2015.

2\. Point b Clause 2 Article 11 and Article 25 of Decree No. [95/2013/ND-CP](https://thuvienphapluat.vn/van-ban/bao-hiem/decree-no-95-2013-nd-cp-administrative-violations-against-regulations-on-labor-206009.aspx "Decree of Government 95/2013/ND-CP") are annulled.

3\. Regulations of the Law on Social insurance 2014 shall apply to interest rates on unpaid social insurance and unemployment insurance mentioned in Point b Clause 4 Article 26 of Decree No. [95/2013/ND-CP](https://thuvienphapluat.vn/van-ban/bao-hiem/decree-no-95-2013-nd-cp-administrative-violations-against-regulations-on-labor-206009.aspx "Decree of Government 95/2013/ND-CP") from January 01, 2016.

4\. Illegally staying in a foreign country after expiration of employment contracts as mentioned in Point a Clause 2 Article 35 of Decree No. [95/2013/ND-CP](https://thuvienphapluat.vn/van-ban/bao-hiem/decree-no-95-2013-nd-cp-administrative-violations-against-regulations-on-labor-206009.aspx "Decree of Government 95/2013/ND-CP") is considered an administrative violation and the time limit for penalty imposition shall begin when the violation is discovered.

5\. Point a Clause 2 Article 28 of Decree No. [95/2013/ND-CP](https://thuvienphapluat.vn/van-ban/bao-hiem/decree-no-95-2013-nd-cp-administrative-violations-against-regulations-on-labor-206009.aspx "Decree of Government 95/2013/ND-CP") , which is amended in this Decree, is annulled from January 01, 2016.

6\. Point b Clause 2 Article 28 of Decree No. [95/2013/ND-CP](https://thuvienphapluat.vn/van-ban/bao-hiem/decree-no-95-2013-nd-cp-administrative-violations-against-regulations-on-labor-206009.aspx "Decree of Government 95/2013/ND-CP") , which is amended in this Decree, is annulled after December 31, 2015; From January 01, 2015, it shall be replaced with this paragraph: “Failure to provide occupational accident benefits or occupational diseases benefits within 10 days from the day on which money is paid by the social insurance agency.”

**Article 3. Implementation**

Ministers, Heads of ministerial agencies, Heads of Governmental agencies, Presidents of the People’s Committees of provinces are responsible for implementation of this Decree./.

